  <entry>
    <title>使用 Hexo 快速搭建博客(Windows 篇)</title>
    <url>/2024/08/21/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-Hexo-%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>如何使用 Hexo 快速搭建属于自己的博客</p>
<h2 id="官方文档"><a href="#官方文档" class="headerlink" title="官方文档"></a>官方文档</h2><ul>
<li><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL3poLWNu">Hexo<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="所需环境："><a href="#所需环境：" class="headerlink" title="所需环境："></a>所需环境：</h2><ul>
<li><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cDovL25vZGVqcy5vcmcv">Node.js<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span>(Node.js 版本需不低于 10.13，建议使用 Node.js 12.0 及以上版本)</li>
<li><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cDovL2dpdC1zY20uY29tLw==">Git<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></li>
</ul>
<span id="more"></span>

<p>本文章使用的环境版本<br><code>node.js v14.18.2</code><br><code>git v2.34.1.windows.1</code><br><code>hexo v7.3.0</code><br><code>hexo-cli v4.3.2</code></p>
<h2 id="为什么用-Hexo"><a href="#为什么用-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="为什么用 Hexo"></a>为什么用 Hexo</h2><p>速度 <strong>快</strong>、<strong>简洁</strong> 且 <strong>高效</strong>，<strong>插件多</strong>，使用 <strong>MarkDown</strong> 语法</p>
<h2 id="安装-Hexo"><a href="#安装-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装 Hexo"></a>安装 Hexo</h2><p>执行以下步骤默认已安装好了 <strong>node</strong>，<strong>git</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight cmd"><figcaption><span>cmd</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>解释：</strong>-g 全局安装</p>
<h2 id="版本限制"><a href="#版本限制" class="headerlink" title="版本限制"></a>版本限制</h2><ul>
<li><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL3poLWNuL2RvY3MvI05vZGUtanMtJUU3JTg5JTg4JUU2JTlDJUFDJUU5JTk5JTkwJUU1JTg4JUI2">这里查看<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="搭建博客"><a href="#搭建博客" class="headerlink" title="搭建博客"></a>搭建博客</h2><p>在所需目录使用 <strong>git</strong> 打开</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>git</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">cd &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>解释：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>&lt;folder&gt;：替换成自己所需的文件名</li>
<li>hexo init &lt;folder&gt;：初始化博客文件夹</li>
<li>cd &lt;folder&gt;：进入博客文件夹</li>
<li>npm install：加载所需的依赖</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="博客文件夹目录"><a href="#博客文件夹目录" class="headerlink" title="博客文件夹目录"></a>博客文件夹目录</h2><ul>
<li><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL3poLWNuL2RvY3Mvc2V0dXA=">详细说明<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.</span><br><span class="line">├── node_modules</span><br><span class="line">├── scaffolds</span><br><span class="line">├── source</span><br><span class="line">|   └── _posts</span><br><span class="line">├── _config.yml</span><br><span class="line">├── package.json</span><br><span class="line">└── themes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<strong>解释：</strong></li>
<li>node_modules：插件目录</li>
<li>scaffolds：模板文件夹</li>
<li>source：资源文件夹</li>
<li>_config.yml：站点配置文件</li>
<li>package.json：引用程序的信息</li>
<li>themes：主题文件夹</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="基础配置"><a href="#基础配置" class="headerlink" title="基础配置"></a>基础配置</h2><ul>
<li><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL3poLWNuL2RvY3MvY29uZmlndXJhdGlvbg==">详细配置<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">网站标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">网站副标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">网站描述</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">名字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">语言</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">default_layout:</span> <span class="string">预设布局</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">主题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span> <span class="string">github</span> <span class="string">等部署</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<strong>解释：</strong>语言需要配合主题使用</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="命令"><a href="#命令" class="headerlink" title="命令"></a>命令</h2><ul>
<li><p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL3poLWNuL2RvY3MvY29tbWFuZHM=">详细命令<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>git</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new &lt;title&gt;</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>解释：</strong></p>
</li>
<li><p>hexo new &lt;title&gt;：使用默认布局创建帖子</p>
</li>
<li><p>hexo clean：清除缓存</p>
</li>
<li><p>hexo generate：生成 public 文件（静态文件）</p>
</li>
<li><p>hexo deploy：推送到 github 等仓库（需要配置 deploy）</p>
</li>
<li><p>hexo server：本地运行</p>
</li>
<li><p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL3poLWNu">更多设置请参考官方文档<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
